[Server 17:37:22.66 INFO]: Pomni: (narrating) Pomni; Abigail Brooks. She's still an accountant, but she seems to have opened up more and is hanging out with new friends more often. She even has some of them in her videos with her, which she still posts on occasion.
[Server 17:37:52.49 INFO]: Pomni: Ragatha; Suzie J. Ackerman. She appears to have left her hometown, cut all communication with her mother and has excelled in her career. She's made many friends, and it looks like she has a strong genuine connection with them. She seems happy, like she understands who she is and that she matters to people.
[Server 17:38:17.74 INFO]: Pomni: Gangle; Zoey Raghavan. Despite her injuries, she's made a good recovery in the hospital. She quit her fast food job and has gotten a new job at a small design firm.
[Server 17:38:36.27 INFO]: Pomni: She even began posting pages of her webcomic online.
[Server 17:38:38.12 INFO]: Pomni: Zooble; Riley Verselis. After hopping around with different jobs, they look like they've settled a bit and opened their own bar. It seems to be a successful one. People all over the city come to it as a hip alternative destination, where they can feel like themselves, free of judgment.
[Server 17:38:57.42 INFO]: Pomni: Kinger; Grant Best. He's still working in tech and is still happily married to his wife, Destiny. They appear to have two daughters together. He looks like he's a good dad.
[Server 17:39:34.01 INFO]: Pomni: Jax; Leeroy Mateo. After being unhoused for a few months, he was able to room with one of his close friends. He seems to have gotten a stable job and is able to pay rent. He and his friends go out every now and again. Weirdly enough, a spot they seem to frequent is Riley's bar.
[Server 17:40:05.20 INFO]: Zooble: Is any of this actually real?
[Server 17:40:07.37 INFO]: Gangle: You definitely have it in you. Not sure about mine though.
[Server 17:40:11.91 INFO]: Zooble: Well, maybe you've got more confidence than you thought.
[Server 17:40:18.90 INFO]: Caine: I don't quite have the same power that I used to, but I can still make this place better for you. I'm keeping the worlds open, so you can do what you want when you feel like it.
[Server 17:40:43.27 INFO]: Caine: You're gonna be able to build this place into something better. For all of you. What do you say, Pom- uh, I mean, Abigail?
[Server 17:40:49.86 INFO]: Pomni: With all that being said and done, Abby is out there, living her best life. In here, I'm just Pomni.
